          <title>Nikola Jokic hits 66-foot heave to highlight his 5th straight triple-double</title>
          <description><![CDATA[DENVER (AP) — Nikola Jokic took an inbounds pass with 1.7 seconds left in the third quarter, turned and let fly with a 66-foot heave that got all net at the other end. He casually walked over to his bench as his teammates mobbed him and the sold-out arena erupted.]]></description>
